## Monitoring

To deliver continuous improvement we:

- monitor the performance of our content and services, this forms part of <%= external_link("https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/agile-delivery/running-your-service-in-a-sustainable-way", "maintaining a sustainable service (opens in new tab)")%>
- <%= external_link("https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/measuring-success/how-to-set-performance-metrics-for-your-service", "set key performance indicators (KPIs) (opens in new tab)")%> and measure our content or service against those indicators on a regular basis
- have a plan in place for how we will develop and test content through its life cycle
- use Google Analytics, set up dashboards to measure against KPIs and set regular reports
- build in ways for users to give feedback
- identify ways to trigger alerts to issues with content and how to address them
  

